  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Social and Economic Integration of Ex-Combatants and Strengthening of Receiving Communities</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The primary objective of this project is to contribute to a timely, safe and orderly return and reintegration of ex-combatants and their dependents in their place of origin or in a place of their choice in Ethiopia. It promotes community-based reintegration approaches and focuses on two pillars: economic and social reintegration. Individual economic integration activities have been the focus of program activities and are designed to enhance the economic wellbeing of the ex-combatants, as to reduce drivers for re-mobilization.</narrative>
  </description>
